{"tid":1449693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"表揚警察應該由家屬入手","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:15:23.000Z","uid":59818,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f26a48c6e468dcdf4d3da66909469f90e6ffe172","tid":1449693,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"呢排香港咁混亂 全靠香港警察<br />\n見大家都好想表揚佢地<br />\n<br />\n但其實更應該佢地屋企人入手<br />\n難得暑假 好多當差嘅都要ot <br />\n仔仔同老婆都好寂寞 好應該關心下佢地<br />\n<br />\n呢排有好多質疑警方嘅聲音 令到呢啲家屬都唔敢比人知有屋企人係當差<br />\n<br />\n我地可以到佢地屋企/公作地點樓下大聲開名宣揚佢地老豆/老公對香港嘅貢獻<br />\n比佢地嘅鄰居同事知道 多啲關心佢地"},{"pid":"de9577ad4c09d90be12d252d9473f7cfeae7d4d4","tid":1449693,"uid":261433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:49.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a8d71e3114ba385531b6f6f9fb18abc7e3180c6e","tid":1449693,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032593f404e08c50f81b48355d100f1554326411","tid":1449693,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72beb2e9beacadadcb82875046bdac51d42c622","tid":1449693,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f117380b06894fa3b7d691b6acadc3c9fbabc43b","tid":1449693,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedf61e68df45e4b7c0cff0d961098ea0f5b5967","tid":1449693,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:07:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32344392cdd79fd20b03519ba12885e23ee74c78","tid":1449693,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":